        public JSONRequest createRequest(SocketChannel channel,
                                 byte[] data)
                          throws IOException
        Description copied from class: Router
        Creates a concrete request from given data. The request is bound to given channel. The response the given request is sent to the same channel.
        A request specifies a grammar or format. A HTTP request, for example, will start with a status line, followed by headers etc. This method is responsible to create such a request from given raw byte data.
